testcase.name: Step 1: Verify multiple trends load in drop down menu
Step 2: Change time range to less than 4 days and verify switch to higher frequency data
Step 3: Change time range with handles and by typing date range in calendar
Step 4: Change scale of axes, click ok, verify
Step 5: Change scale of axes back to auto, click ok, verify
Step 6: Verify Hamburger Chart button exists and functions as desired- save chart as all 4 types and print preview
Step 8: Expand chart to full screen
Step 9: Verify "click and drag" zoom works properly
Step 10: Click on chart editor button and verify that it navigates to correct chart and time range
